数据库导入导出搜索路径

show variables like "secure_file_priv";
＃通过该命令可以查看搜索路径

修改搜索路径
vim /etc/my.cnf
[mysqld]
secure_file_pri="/mydir"
#配置文件中添加这一行

mkdir /mydir
chown mysql /mudir
mysql用户需要对/mydir有写权限

修改完重启服务
systemctl restart mysqld

###############################################

数据导入：
把系统文件的内容存储到数据库的表里
命令用法：
mysql> load data infile ""　into table 表名
　　　　fields terminated by "分隔符"
       lines  terminated by "\n";
例子:
mysql> load data infile "/mydir/passwd" into user
       fields terminated by ":"
       lines terminated by "\n";
＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃

数据导出：
把表的记录存到系统文件里
命令用法：
SQL查询 into outfile "目录名/文件名";
SQL查询 into outfile "目录名/文件名" fields terminated by "分隔符";
SQL查询 into outfile "目录名/文件名" lines terminated by "分隔符";
例子：
select * from user where id<=2 into outfile "/mydir/user.txt"；

